Title: At Any Price
Actors: Dennis Quaid, Kim Dickens, Aaron B. Oduber, Jacob R. Oduber
Plot: In the competitive world of modern agriculture, ambitious Henry Whipple wants his rebellious son Dean to help expand his family's farming empire. However, Dean has his sights set on becoming a professional race car driver. When a high-stakes investigation into their business is exposed, father and son are pushed into an unexpected crisis that threatens the family's entire livelihood.
